    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The process of fine detailed “cold work” after casting and fettlingthat serves to correct or enhance the cast surface by removingand/or compressing metal using hand tools by punching,engraving, and/or chiseling, and in modern times also with powerand pneumatic tools.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
